 617     @Override                                                                                            
 618     public FieldMetadata cloneFieldMetadata() {                                                          
 619         BasicFieldMetadata metadata = new BasicFieldMetadata();                                          
 620         metadata.fieldType = fieldType;                                                                  
 621         metadata.secondaryType = secondaryType;                                                          
 622         metadata.length = length;                                                                        
 623         metadata.required = required;                                                                    
 624         metadata.unique = unique;                                                                        
 625         metadata.scale = scale;                                                                          
 626         metadata.precision = precision;                                                                  
 627         metadata.mutable = mutable;                                                                      
 628         metadata.foreignKeyProperty = foreignKeyProperty;                                                
 629         metadata.foreignKeyClass = foreignKeyClass;                                                      
 630         metadata.foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty = foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty;                        
 631         metadata.foreignKeyCollection = foreignKeyCollection;                                            
 632         metadata.mergedPropertyType = mergedPropertyType;                                                
 633         metadata.enumerationClass = enumerationClass;                                                    
 634         if (enumerationValues != null) {                                                                 
 635             metadata.enumerationValues = new String[enumerationValues.length][];                         
 636             for (int j=0;j<enumerationValues.length;j++) {                                               
 637                 metadata.enumerationValues[j] = new String[enumerationValues[j].length];                 
 638                 System.arraycopy(enumerationValues[j], 0, metadata.enumerationValues[j], 0, enumerationVaðŸ”µ
 639             }                                                                                            
 640         }                                                                                                
 641                                                                                                          
 642         metadata.name = name;                                                                            
 643         metadata.visibility = visibility;                                                                
 644         metadata.groupCollapsed = groupCollapsed;                                                        
 645         metadata.explicitFieldType = explicitFieldType;                                                  
 646         metadata.displayType = displayType;                                                              
 647         metadata.largeEntry = largeEntry;                                                                
 648         metadata.prominent = prominent;                                                                  
 649         metadata.gridOrder = gridOrder;                                                                  
 650         metadata.columnWidth = columnWidth;                                                              
 651         metadata.broadleafEnumeration = broadleafEnumeration;                                            
 652         metadata.hideEnumerationIfEmpty = hideEnumerationIfEmpty;                                        
 653         metadata.fieldComponentRenderer = fieldComponentRenderer;                                        
 654         metadata.fieldComponentRendererTemplate = fieldComponentRendererTemplate;                        
 655         metadata.gridFieldComponentRenderer = gridFieldComponentRenderer;                                
 656         metadata.gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate = gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate;                
 657         metadata.readOnly = readOnly;                                                                    
 658         metadata.requiredOverride = requiredOverride;                                                    
 659         metadata.tooltip = tooltip;                                                                      
 660         metadata.helpText = helpText;                                                                    
 661         metadata.hint = hint;                                                                            
 662         for (Map.Entry<String, List<Map<String, String>>> entry : validationConfigurations.entrySet()) { 
 663             List<Map<String, String>> clonedConfigItems = new ArrayList<>(entry.getValue().size());      
 664                                                                                                          
 665             for (Map<String, String> configEntries : entry.getValue()) {                                 
 666                 Map<String, String> clone = new HashMap<>(configEntries.keySet().size());                
 667                 for (Map.Entry<String, String> entry2 : configEntries.entrySet()) {                      
 668                     clone.put(entry2.getKey(), entry2.getValue());                                       
 669                 }                                                                                        
 670                 clonedConfigItems.add(clone);                                                            
 671             }                                                                                            
 672             metadata.validationConfigurations.put(entry.getKey(), clonedConfigItems);                    
 673         }                                                                                                
 674         metadata.lookupDisplayProperty = lookupDisplayProperty;                                          
 675         metadata.forcePopulateChildProperties = forcePopulateChildProperties;                            
 676         metadata.enableTypeaheadLookup = enableTypeaheadLookup;                                          
 677         metadata.optionListEntity = optionListEntity;                                                    
 678         metadata.optionCanEditValues = optionCanEditValues;                                              
 679         metadata.optionHideIfEmpty = optionHideIfEmpty;                                                  
 680         metadata.optionDisplayFieldName = optionDisplayFieldName;                                        
 681         metadata.optionValueFieldName = optionValueFieldName;                                            
 682         if (optionFilterParams != null) {                                                                
 683             metadata.optionFilterParams = new String[optionFilterParams.length][];                       
 684             for (int j=0;j<optionFilterParams.length;j++) {                                              
 685                 metadata.optionFilterParams[j] = new String[optionFilterParams[j].length];               
 686                 System.arraycopy(optionFilterParams[j], 0, metadata.optionFilterParams[j], 0, optionFilteðŸ”µ
 687             }                                                                                            
 688         }                                                                                                
 689         metadata.customCriteria = customCriteria;                                                        
 690         metadata.useServerSideInspectionCache = useServerSideInspectionCache;                            
 691         metadata.toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation = toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation;                      
 692         metadata.ruleIdentifier = ruleIdentifier;                                                        
 693         metadata.mapFieldValueClass = mapFieldValueClass;                                                
 694         metadata.searchable = searchable;                                                                
 695         metadata.manyToField = manyToField;                                                              
 696         metadata.toOneTargetProperty = toOneTargetProperty;                                              
 697         metadata.toOneParentProperty = toOneParentProperty;                                              
 698         metadata.mapKeyValueProperty = mapKeyValueProperty;                                              
 699         metadata.lookupType = lookupType;                                                                
 700         metadata.translatable = translatable;                                                            
 701         metadata.isDerived = isDerived;                                                                  
 702         metadata.defaultValue = defaultValue;                                                            
 703         metadata.associatedFieldName = associatedFieldName;                                              
 704         metadata.canLinkToExternalEntity = canLinkToExternalEntity;                                      
 705                                                                                                          
 706         metadata = (BasicFieldMetadata) populate(metadata);                                              
 707                                                                                                          
 708         return metadata;                                                                                 
 709     }                                                                                                    
 710                                                                                                          
 711     @Override                                                                                            
 712     public void accept(MetadataVisitor visitor) {                                                        
 713         visitor.visit(this);

 677     @Override                                                                                            
 678     public FieldMetadata cloneFieldMetadata() {                                                          
 679         BasicFieldMetadata metadata = new BasicFieldMetadata();                                          
 680         metadata.fieldType = fieldType;                                                                  
 681         metadata.secondaryType = secondaryType;                                                          
 682         metadata.length = length;                                                                        
 683         metadata.required = required;                                                                    
 684         metadata.unique = unique;                                                                        
 685         metadata.scale = scale;                                                                          
 686         metadata.precision = precision;                                                                  
 687         metadata.mutable = mutable;                                                                      
 688         metadata.foreignKeyProperty = foreignKeyProperty;                                                
 689         metadata.foreignKeyClass = foreignKeyClass;                                                      
 690         metadata.foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty = foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty;                        
 691         metadata.foreignKeyCollection = foreignKeyCollection;                                            
 692         metadata.mergedPropertyType = mergedPropertyType;                                                
 693         metadata.enumerationClass = enumerationClass;                                                    
 694         if (enumerationValues != null) {                                                                 
 695             metadata.enumerationValues = new String[enumerationValues.length][];                         
 696             for (int j=0;j<enumerationValues.length;j++) {                                               
 697                 metadata.enumerationValues[j] = new String[enumerationValues[j].length];                 
 698                 System.arraycopy(enumerationValues[j], 0, metadata.enumerationValues[j], 0, enumerationVaðŸ”µ
 699             }                                                                                            
 700         }                                                                                                
 701                                                                                                          
 702         metadata.name = name;                                                                            
 703         metadata.visibility = visibility;                                                                
 704         metadata.groupCollapsed = groupCollapsed;                                                        
 705         metadata.explicitFieldType = explicitFieldType;                                                  
 706         metadata.displayType = displayType;                                                              
 707         metadata.largeEntry = largeEntry;                                                                
 708         metadata.prominent = prominent;                                                                  
 709         metadata.gridOrder = gridOrder;                                                                  
 710         metadata.columnWidth = columnWidth;                                                              
 711         metadata.broadleafEnumeration = broadleafEnumeration;                                            
 712         metadata.hideEnumerationIfEmpty = hideEnumerationIfEmpty;                                        
 713         metadata.fieldComponentRenderer = fieldComponentRenderer;                                        
 714         metadata.fieldComponentRendererTemplate = fieldComponentRendererTemplate;                        
 715         metadata.gridFieldComponentRenderer = gridFieldComponentRenderer;                                
 716         metadata.gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate = gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate;                
 717         metadata.readOnly = readOnly;                                                                    
 718         metadata.requiredOverride = requiredOverride;                                                    
 719         metadata.tooltip = tooltip;                                                                      
 720         metadata.helpText = helpText;                                                                    
 721         metadata.hint = hint;                                                                            
 722         for (Map.Entry<String, List<Map<String, String>>> entry : validationConfigurations.entrySet()) { 
 723             List<Map<String, String>> clonedConfigItems = new ArrayList<>(entry.getValue().size());      
 724                                                                                                          
 725             for (Map<String, String> configEntries : entry.getValue()) {                                 
 726                 Map<String, String> clone = new HashMap<>(configEntries.keySet().size());                
 727                 for (Map.Entry<String, String> entry2 : configEntries.entrySet()) {                      
 728                     clone.put(entry2.getKey(), entry2.getValue());                                       
 729                 }                                                                                        
 730                 clonedConfigItems.add(clone);                                                            
 731             }                                                                                            
 732             metadata.validationConfigurations.put(entry.getKey(), clonedConfigItems);                    
 733         }                                                                                                
 734         metadata.lookupDisplayProperty = lookupDisplayProperty;                                          
 735         metadata.forcePopulateChildProperties = forcePopulateChildProperties;                            
 736         metadata.enableTypeaheadLookup = enableTypeaheadLookup;                                          
 737         metadata.optionListEntity = optionListEntity;                                                    
 738         metadata.optionCanEditValues = optionCanEditValues;                                              
 739         metadata.optionHideIfEmpty = optionHideIfEmpty;                                                  
 740         metadata.optionDisplayFieldName = optionDisplayFieldName;                                        
 741         metadata.optionValueFieldName = optionValueFieldName;                                            
 742         if (optionFilterParams != null) {                                                                
 743             metadata.optionFilterParams = new String[optionFilterParams.length][];                       
 744             for (int j=0;j<optionFilterParams.length;j++) {                                              
 745                 metadata.optionFilterParams[j] = new String[optionFilterParams[j].length];               
 746                 System.arraycopy(optionFilterParams[j], 0, metadata.optionFilterParams[j], 0, optionFilteðŸ”µ
 747             }                                                                                            
 748         }                                                                                                
 749         metadata.customCriteria = customCriteria;                                                        
 750         metadata.useServerSideInspectionCache = useServerSideInspectionCache;                            
 751         metadata.toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation = toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation;                      
 752         metadata.ruleIdentifier = ruleIdentifier;                                                        
 753         metadata.mapFieldValueClass = mapFieldValueClass;                                                
 754         metadata.searchable = searchable;                                                                
 755         metadata.manyToField = manyToField;                                                              
 756         metadata.toOneTargetProperty = toOneTargetProperty;                                              
 757         metadata.toOneParentProperty = toOneParentProperty;                                              
 758         metadata.mapKeyValueProperty = mapKeyValueProperty;                                              
 759         metadata.lookupType = lookupType;                                                                
 760         metadata.translatable = translatable;                                                            
 761         metadata.isDerived = isDerived;                                                                  
 762         metadata.defaultValue = defaultValue;                                                            
 763         metadata.associatedFieldName = associatedFieldName;                                              
 764         metadata.canLinkToExternalEntity = canLinkToExternalEntity;                                      
 765                                                                                                          
 766         metadata = (BasicFieldMetadata) populate(metadata);                                              
 767                                                                                                          
 768         return metadata;                                                                                 
 769     }

 776     @Override                                                                                            
 777     public boolean equals(Object o) {                                                                    
 778         if (this == o) {                                                                                 
 779             return true;                                                                                 
 780         }                                                                                                
 781         if (o == null) {                                                                                 
 782             return false;                                                                                
 783         }                                                                                                
 784         if (!getClass().isAssignableFrom(o.getClass())) {                                                
 785             return false;                                                                                
 786         }                                                                                                
 787         if (!super.equals(o)) {                                                                          
 788             return false;                                                                                
 789         }                                                                                                
 790                                                                                                          
 791         BasicFieldMetadata metadata = (BasicFieldMetadata) o;                                            
 792                                                                                                          
 793         if (broadleafEnumeration != null ? !broadleafEnumeration.equals(metadata.broadleafEnumeration) : ðŸ”µ
 794             return false;                                                                                
 795         }                                                                                                
 796         if (hideEnumerationIfEmpty != null ? !hideEnumerationIfEmpty.equals(metadata.hideEnumerationIfEmpðŸ”µ
 797             return false;                                                                                
 798         }                                                                                                
 799         if (fieldComponentRenderer != null ? !fieldComponentRenderer.equals(metadata.fieldComponentRenderðŸ”µ
 800             return false;                                                                                
 801         }                                                                                                
 802         if (fieldComponentRendererTemplate != null ? !fieldComponentRendererTemplate.equals(metadata.fielðŸ”µ
 803             return false;                                                                                
 804         }                                                                                                
 805         if (gridFieldComponentRenderer != null ? !gridFieldComponentRenderer.equals(metadata.gridFieldComðŸ”µ
 806             return false;                                                                                
 807         }                                                                                                
 808         if (gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate != null ? !gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate.equals(metadðŸ”µ
 809             return false;                                                                                
 810         }                                                                                                
 811         if (columnWidth != null ? !columnWidth.equals(metadata.columnWidth) : metadata.columnWidth != nulðŸ”µ
 812             return false;                                                                                
 813         }                                                                                                
 814         if (enumerationClass != null ? !enumerationClass.equals(metadata.enumerationClass) : metadata.enuðŸ”µ
 815             return false;                                                                                
 816         }                                                                                                
 817         if (explicitFieldType != metadata.explicitFieldType) {                                           
 818             return false;                                                                                
 819         }                                                                                                
 820         if (displayType != metadata.displayType) {                                                       
 821             return false;                                                                                
 822         }                                                                                                
 823         if (fieldType != metadata.fieldType) {                                                           
 824             return false;                                                                                
 825         }                                                                                                
 826         if (foreignKeyClass != null ? !foreignKeyClass.equals(metadata.foreignKeyClass) : metadata.foreigðŸ”µ
 827             return false;                                                                                
 828         }                                                                                                
 829         if (foreignKeyCollection != null ? !foreignKeyCollection.equals(metadata.foreignKeyCollection) : ðŸ”µ
 830             return false;                                                                                
 831         }                                                                                                
 832         if (foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty != null ? !foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty.equals(metadata.foreðŸ”µ
 833             return false;                                                                                
 834         }                                                                                                
 835         if (foreignKeyProperty != null ? !foreignKeyProperty.equals(metadata.foreignKeyProperty) : metadaðŸ”µ
 836             return false;                                                                                
 837         }                                                                                                
 838         if (groupCollapsed != null ? !groupCollapsed.equals(metadata.groupCollapsed) : metadata.groupCollðŸ”µ
 839             return false;                                                                                
 840         }                                                                                                
 841         if (helpText != null ? !helpText.equals(metadata.helpText) : metadata.helpText != null) {        
 842             return false;                                                                                
 843         }                                                                                                
 844         if (hint != null ? !hint.equals(metadata.hint) : metadata.hint != null) {                        
 845             return false;                                                                                
 846         }                                                                                                
 847         if (largeEntry != null ? !largeEntry.equals(metadata.largeEntry) : metadata.largeEntry != null) {
 848             return false;                                                                                
 849         }                                                                                                
 850         if (length != null ? !length.equals(metadata.length) : metadata.length != null) {

 618      @Override                                                                                                     
 619      public FieldMetadata cloneFieldMetadata() {                                                                   
 620          BasicFieldMetadata metadata = new BasicFieldMetadata();                                                   
 621          metadata.fieldType = fieldType;                                                                           
 622          metadata.secondaryType = secondaryType;                                                                   
 623          metadata.length = length;                                                                                 
 624          metadata.required = required;                                                                             
 625          metadata.unique = unique;                                                                                 
 626          metadata.scale = scale;                                                                                   
 627          metadata.precision = precision;                                                                           
 628          metadata.mutable = mutable;                                                                               
 629          metadata.foreignKeyProperty = foreignKeyProperty;                                                         
 630          metadata.foreignKeyClass = foreignKeyClass;                                                               
 631          metadata.foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty = foreignKeyDisplayValueProperty;                                 
 632          metadata.foreignKeyCollection = foreignKeyCollection;                                                     
 633          metadata.mergedPropertyType = mergedPropertyType;                                                         
 634          metadata.enumerationClass = enumerationClass;                                                             
 635          if (enumerationValues != null) {                                                                          
 636              metadata.enumerationValues = new String[enumerationValues.length][];                                  
 637              for (int j=0;j<enumerationValues.length;j++) {                                                        
 638                  metadata.enumerationValues[j] = new String[enumerationValues[j].length];                          
 639                  System.arraycopy(enumerationValues[j], 0, metadata.enumerationValues[j], 0, enumerationValues[j].lðŸ”µ
 640              }                                                                                                     
 641          }                                                                                                         
 642                                                                                                                    
 643          metadata.name = name;                                                                                     
 644          metadata.visibility = visibility;                                                                         
 645          metadata.groupCollapsed = groupCollapsed;                                                                 
 646          metadata.explicitFieldType = explicitFieldType;                                                           
 647          metadata.displayType = displayType;                                                                       
 648          metadata.largeEntry = largeEntry;                                                                         
 649          metadata.prominent = prominent;                                                                           
 650          metadata.gridOrder = gridOrder;                                                                           
 651          metadata.columnWidth = columnWidth;                                                                       
 652          metadata.broadleafEnumeration = broadleafEnumeration;                                                     
 653          metadata.hideEnumerationIfEmpty = hideEnumerationIfEmpty;                                                 
 654          metadata.fieldComponentRenderer = fieldComponentRenderer;                                                 
 655          metadata.fieldComponentRendererTemplate = fieldComponentRendererTemplate;                                 
 656          metadata.gridFieldComponentRenderer = gridFieldComponentRenderer;                                         
 657          metadata.gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate = gridFieldComponentRendererTemplate;                         
 658          metadata.readOnly = readOnly;                                                                             
 659          metadata.requiredOverride = requiredOverride;                                                             
 660          metadata.tooltip = tooltip;                                                                               
 661          metadata.helpText = helpText;                                                                             
 662          metadata.hint = hint;                                                                                     
 663          for (Map.Entry<String, List<Map<String, String>>> entry : validationConfigurations.entrySet()) {          
 664              List<Map<String, String>> clonedConfigItems = new ArrayList<>(entry.getValue().size());               
 665                                                                                                                    
 666              for (Map<String, String> configEntries : entry.getValue()) {                                          
 667                  Map<String, String> clone = new HashMap<>(configEntries.keySet().size());                         
 668                  for (Map.Entry<String, String> entry2 : configEntries.entrySet()) {                               
 669                      clone.put(entry2.getKey(), entry2.getValue());                                                
 670                  }                                                                                                 
 671                  clonedConfigItems.add(clone);                                                                     
 672              }                                                                                                     
 673              metadata.validationConfigurations.put(entry.getKey(), clonedConfigItems);                             
 674          }                                                                                                         
 675          metadata.lookupDisplayProperty = lookupDisplayProperty;                                                   
 676          metadata.forcePopulateChildProperties = forcePopulateChildProperties;                                     
 677          metadata.enableTypeaheadLookup = enableTypeaheadLookup;                                                   
 678          metadata.optionListEntity = optionListEntity;                                                             
 679          metadata.optionCanEditValues = optionCanEditValues;                                                       
 680          metadata.optionHideIfEmpty = optionHideIfEmpty;                                                           
 681          metadata.optionDisplayFieldName = optionDisplayFieldName;                                                 
 682          metadata.optionValueFieldName = optionValueFieldName;                                                     
 683          if (optionFilterParams != null) {                                                                         
 684              metadata.optionFilterParams = new String[optionFilterParams.length][];                                
 685              for (int j=0;j<optionFilterParams.length;j++) {                                                       
 686                  metadata.optionFilterParams[j] = new String[optionFilterParams[j].length];                        
 687                  System.arraycopy(optionFilterParams[j], 0, metadata.optionFilterParams[j], 0, optionFilterParams[jðŸ”µ
 688              }                                                                                                     
 689          }                                                                                                         
 690          metadata.customCriteria = customCriteria;                                                                 
 691          metadata.useServerSideInspectionCache = useServerSideInspectionCache;                                     
 692          metadata.toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation = toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation;                               
 693          metadata.ruleIdentifier = ruleIdentifier;                                                                 
 694          metadata.mapFieldValueClass = mapFieldValueClass;                                                         
 695          metadata.searchable = searchable;                                                                         
 696          metadata.manyToField = manyToField;                                                                       
 697          metadata.toOneTargetProperty = toOneTargetProperty;                                                       
 698          metadata.toOneParentProperty = toOneParentProperty;                                                       
 699          metadata.mapKeyValueProperty = mapKeyValueProperty;                                                       
 700          metadata.lookupType = lookupType;                                                                         
 701          metadata.translatable = translatable;                                                                     
 702          metadata.isDerived = isDerived;                                                                           
 703          metadata.defaultValue = defaultValue;                                                                     
 704          metadata.associatedFieldName = associatedFieldName;                                                       
 705          metadata.canLinkToExternalEntity = canLinkToExternalEntity;                                               
 706                                                                                                                    
 707          metadata = (BasicFieldMetadata) populate(metadata);                                                       
 708                                                                                                                    
 709          return metadata;                                                                                          
 710      }

 880          }                                                                                                         
 881          if (mapKeyValueProperty != null ? !mapKeyValueProperty.equals(metadata.mapKeyValueProperty) : metadata.mapðŸ”µ
 882              return false;                                                                                         
 883          }                                                                                                         
 884          if (lookupType != null ? !lookupType.equals(metadata.lookupType) : metadata.lookupType != null) {         
 885              return false;                                                                                         
 886          }                                                                                                         
 887          if (isDerived != null ? !isDerived.equals(metadata.isDerived) : metadata.isDerived != null) {             
 888              return false;                                                                                         
 889          }                                                                                                         
 890          if (canLinkToExternalEntity != null ? !canLinkToExternalEntity.equals(metadata.canLinkToExternalEntity) : ðŸ”µ
 891              return false;                                                                                         
 892          }                                                                                                         
 893                                                                                                                    
 894          return true;                                                                                              
 895      }                                                                                                             
 896                                                                                                                    
 897      @Override                                                                                                     
 898      public int hashCode() {

 900          result = 31 * result + (fieldType != null ? fieldType.hashCode() : 0);

 938          result = 31 * result + (optionListEntity != null ? optionListEntity.hashCode() : 0);                      
 939          result = 31 * result + (optionValueFieldName != null ? optionValueFieldName.hashCode() : 0);              
 940          result = 31 * result + (optionDisplayFieldName != null ? optionDisplayFieldName.hashCode() : 0);

 659          metadata.requiredOverride = requiredOverride;                                                             
 660          metadata.tooltip = tooltip;                                                                               
 661          metadata.helpText = helpText;                                                                             
 662          metadata.hint = hint;                                                                                     
 663          for (Map.Entry<String, List<Map<String, String>>> entry : validationConfigurations.entrySet()) {          
 664              List<Map<String, String>> clonedConfigItems = new ArrayList<>(entry.getValue().size());               
 665                                                                                                                    
 666              for (Map<String, String> configEntries : entry.getValue()) {                                          
 667                  Map<String, String> clone = new HashMap<>(configEntries.keySet().size());                         
 668                  for (Map.Entry<String, String> entry2 : configEntries.entrySet()) {                               
 669                      clone.put(entry2.getKey(), entry2.getValue());                                                
 670                  }                                                                                                 
 671                  clonedConfigItems.add(clone);                                                                     
 672              }                                                                                                     
 673              metadata.validationConfigurations.put(entry.getKey(), clonedConfigItems);                             
 674          }                                                                                                         
 675          metadata.lookupDisplayProperty = lookupDisplayProperty;                                                   
 676          metadata.forcePopulateChildProperties = forcePopulateChildProperties;                                     
 677          metadata.enableTypeaheadLookup = enableTypeaheadLookup;                                                   
 678          metadata.optionListEntity = optionListEntity;                                                             
 679          metadata.optionCanEditValues = optionCanEditValues;                                                       
 680          metadata.optionHideIfEmpty = optionHideIfEmpty;                                                           
 681          metadata.optionDisplayFieldName = optionDisplayFieldName;                                                 
 682          metadata.optionValueFieldName = optionValueFieldName;                                                     
 683          if (optionFilterParams != null) {                                                                         
 684              metadata.optionFilterParams = new String[optionFilterParams.length][];                                
 685              for (int j=0;j<optionFilterParams.length;j++) {                                                       
 686                  metadata.optionFilterParams[j] = new String[optionFilterParams[j].length];                        
 687                  System.arraycopy(optionFilterParams[j], 0, metadata.optionFilterParams[j], 0, optionFilterParams[jðŸ”µ
 688              }                                                                                                     
 689          }                                                                                                         
 690          metadata.customCriteria = customCriteria;                                                                 
 691          metadata.useServerSideInspectionCache = useServerSideInspectionCache;                                     
 692          metadata.toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation = toOneLookupCreatedViaAnnotation;                               
 693          metadata.ruleIdentifier = ruleIdentifier;                                                                 
 694          metadata.mapFieldValueClass = mapFieldValueClass;                                                         
 695          metadata.searchable = searchable;                                                                         
 696          metadata.manyToField = manyToField;                                                                       
 697          metadata.toOneTargetProperty = toOneTargetProperty;                                                       
 698          metadata.toOneParentProperty = toOneParentProperty;                                                       
 699          metadata.mapKeyValueProperty = mapKeyValueProperty;                                                       
 700          metadata.lookupType = lookupType;                                                                         
 701          metadata.translatable = translatable;                                                                     
 702          metadata.isDerived = isDerived;                                                                           
 703          metadata.defaultValue = defaultValue;                                                                     
 704          metadata.associatedFieldName = associatedFieldName;                                                       
 705          metadata.canLinkToExternalEntity = canLinkToExternalEntity;
